<!DOCTYPE html>
<title>ImageOptim online</title>
<style>
label {font-weight: bold}
.color {color: #906;}
.hdpi label {font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 200; color: #444;}
.format label {font-weight: normal; font-size: 0.8em}
html {
    background: #ccc;
    color: #000;
    font: 0.9em/1.5 Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    min-height: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
}
body {
    width: 70%;
    top: 15%;
    position: absolute;
    left: 15%;
    height: 70%;
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    background-color: #eee;
    border-radius: 4px;
}
h1 {
    margin: 0 0 1em;
    text-shadow: -1px -1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.15), 1px 1px 1px white;
}
body > form {
    position: absolute;
    top:0; left:0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    padding: 1em;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
    cursor: pointer;
    overflow: auto;
}
hr {
    border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
}
</style>
<script>
function disableSubmit(form) {
    setTimeout(function(){form.elements.s.disabled=true},1);
    setTimeout(function(){form.elements.s.disabled=false},3000);
}
</script>
<body>
<form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data"
    onsubmit="disableSubmit(this)"
    onclick="if (event.target.tagName != 'INPUT' &amp;&amp; event.target.tagName != 'LABEL' &amp;&amp; event.target.tagName != 'A') this.elements.file.click()">
<h1>JPEG and PNG compressors with special secret artisan-crafted settings</h1>
<p><label>Quality: <input name="quality" value="low" type="radio"> Low (smallest file)</label>
<label><input name="quality" value="medium" checked type="radio"> Medium</label>
<label><input name="quality" value="high" type="radio"> High (largest file)</label>
</p>
<p class="hdpi"><label><input name="highdpi" type="checkbox"> High DPI mode (assume pixels are smaller or image is going to be scaled down)</label></p>
<p class="color"><label>Color quality: <input name="chroma_quality" value="low" type="radio"> Messy</label>
<label><input name="chroma_quality" value="auto" checked type="radio"> Auto</label>
<label><input name="chroma_quality" value="high" type="radio"> Sharp (larger file)</label>
</p>
<p class="format"><label>Format: <input name="format" value="jpeg" type="radio"> JPEG</label> <label><input name="format" value="png" checked type="radio"> PNG</label> <label><input name="format" value="" checked type="radio"> <abbr title="dunno">¯\_(ツ)_/¯</abbr></label></p>
<p>Click to select files (24-bit PNG or very-high-quality JPEG)</p>
<input type="file" name="file" accept="image/*" multiple onchange="this.form.submit();disableSubmit(this.form)" />
<input type="submit" name="s">
<p>Once submitted files will download automatically. Multiple files are supported.</p>
<hr>
<p>Hacked together by <a href="https://kornel.ski">Kornel</a> (<a href="https://twitter.com/kornelski">@kornelski</a>). <a href="https://imageoptim.com/donate.html">Donate</a>. This page uses <a href="https://imageoptim.com/api">ImageOptim API</a>.</p>
</form>

